Demo for HMC6343 chip feautures

KNOWN BUGS
==========

- sometimes on Windows there are problems with COM port: auto-creating of
  another instance of the same, incorrect closing of port... Restart
  computer to fix it.
- after system wake-up port can not be open: no such file message. Disconnect
  device before sleeping mode to fix it.
- use I2C addresses: 0x32/0x33 - factory defaults, but if user change them,
  program will not work
- rotation more then 90 degrees is handled incorrect
